1
00:00:07,180 --> 00:00:10,400
A mirror inside the wedding cake?

2
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:14,210
Yeah!
If you can put a mirror inside of it,

3
00:00:14,210 --> 00:00:17,710
we can bust out, 
straight from mirror dimension!

4
00:00:17,710 --> 00:00:21,090
It'll be be fun and sweet!

5
00:00:21,740 --> 00:00:24,390
You're not here to have fun!

6
00:00:24,390 --> 00:00:27,240
Don't make me repeat myself!
Your job is...

7
00:00:27,240 --> 00:00:30,880
I know!
You want me to break the picture, right?

8
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:35,080
But it won't hurt to have fun while doing it!

9
00:00:35,890 --> 00:00:38,070
Don't be ridiculous!

10
00:00:38,400 --> 00:00:40,870
You want to destroy the wedding cake?

11
00:00:40,870 --> 00:00:45,390
You have no idea how much
Mama's been looking forward to it...

12
00:00:45,390 --> 00:00:48,390
You made the copies of Nami
and the others in the woods, right?

13
00:00:48,390 --> 00:00:49,070
Huh?

14
00:00:49,070 --> 00:00:49,960
Yeah!

15
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:52,800
She can make copies of a person

16
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:56,160
and project them onto other animals!

17
00:01:04,420 --> 00:01:06,540
So what?!

18
00:01:10,060 --> 00:01:14,050
I caught them...
Make them look like me.

19
00:01:14,050 --> 00:01:15,480
What?!

20
00:01:15,870 --> 00:01:17,240
Father!

21
00:01:17,580 --> 00:01:19,480
Oh, you all done?

22
00:01:19,480 --> 00:01:22,000
Everything is ready-rero.

23
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,360
Okay. Good job.

24
00:01:29,690 --> 00:01:31,420
It's on now...

25
00:03:13,880 --> 00:03:18,550
P-People are coming out of the cake!

26
00:03:35,870 --> 00:03:38,270
Oh my! I can't believe it!

27
00:03:39,660 --> 00:03:43,140
Another flashy show...

28
00:03:43,140 --> 00:03:47,280
No, that's not it, Du Feld.
This is big news!

29
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:50,530
He's a pirate from the Worst Generation!

30
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:53,620
Straw Hat Luffy!

31
00:03:53,620 --> 00:03:56,260
The unimaginable is happening!

32
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:58,680
Why is he here?

33
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:02,830
Are they all Straw Hat?

34
00:04:02,830 --> 00:04:04,700
Why are there so many of him?

35
00:04:05,540 --> 00:04:09,360
Run! The cake is collapsing!

36
00:04:09,700 --> 00:04:12,180
What are they?!

37
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:18,900
Straw Hat Luffy?!

38
00:04:23,730 --> 00:04:26,320
That bastard!

39
00:04:30,490 --> 00:04:32,700
Pudding-chan, calm down!

40
00:04:34,790 --> 00:04:38,890
It's finally started...
This is all going to be decided in an instant.

41
00:04:38,890 --> 00:04:40,620
You can do it, Luffy!

42
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:46,340
What's going on, Mont d'Or?!

43
00:04:46,340 --> 00:04:51,270
I thought Straw Hat Luffy and the girl
died in the Prisoner Library!

44
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:53,350
Dammit!

45
00:04:53,980 --> 00:04:57,230
Opera, that dumbass...
He really was lying!

46
00:04:57,230 --> 00:05:01,030
He was trying to cover his own ass!

47
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:11,080
My...

48
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:13,040
precious...

49
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,290
cake is...

50
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:18,650
The cake is...

51
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:23,390
What the...?!

52
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:25,590
She's acting weird...

53
00:05:26,290 --> 00:05:30,800
No... I was looking forward to that...

54
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:35,930
Mama, please keep your composure!
I know how you're feeling.

55
00:05:43,230 --> 00:05:45,940
Cake!

56
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:49,160
Head Chef! Run for it!

57
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:51,390
Mama's acting strange!

58
00:05:53,710 --> 00:05:57,800
Bring me a new cake...!

59
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,420
Th-That's impossible...

60
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:03,170
Life...

61
00:06:03,980 --> 00:06:05,450
or...

62
00:06:05,450 --> 00:06:08,430
wedding cake?!

63
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:13,790
G-Guys...

64
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:16,370
It's her Soul Pocus!

65
00:06:16,370 --> 00:06:19,310
She's going to take their lifespans!
What a scoop!

66
00:06:20,090 --> 00:06:24,780
Big Mom can speak directly
to the human soul's fixation on its own life!

67
00:06:24,780 --> 00:06:28,490
If a person fears death at all,
they'll be vulnerable to it...

68
00:06:28,490 --> 00:06:30,620
Look! That's it!

69
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,960
H... H-Help!

70
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:39,980
No!

71
00:06:45,450 --> 00:06:49,430
If you don't give me what I want,

72
00:06:49,430 --> 00:06:53,260
I'll take your lifespan to make up for it!

73
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,400
Go! Go!

74
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,820
Okay, that way!

75
00:07:07,780 --> 00:07:12,070
That voice...
It sounds like Big Mom's throwing a fit out there!

76
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:14,410
We're pretty desperate in here too!

77
00:07:14,410 --> 00:07:17,410
The situation is messier
than we expected it to be!

78
00:07:17,410 --> 00:07:20,190
I'll make you pay for this!

79
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:23,080
Is that all of them?

80
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,880
This Luffy is the last!

81
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:29,170
All right! Let's go, Pedro!

82
00:07:29,170 --> 00:07:31,880
Yeah! Let's give Luffy some backup!

83
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:38,980
We're going too! To back up Sanji-kun !

84
00:07:39,380 --> 00:07:40,320
Are you ready?

85
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,600
Yeah! I've got my earplugs!

86
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:44,730
We'll rescue Sanji's family!

87
00:07:45,740 --> 00:07:49,320
Okay, we'll leave the rest to you, human scum.

88
00:07:50,280 --> 00:07:52,420
Is he really that bad?

89
00:07:52,420 --> 00:07:54,160
He's the worst!

90
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:07,130
Once I get my heart back,
I'll teach them a lesson...

91
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:17,820
That bastard, Straw Hat...

92
00:08:17,820 --> 00:08:20,060
How dare he mess with me!

93
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,100
You bastard!

94
00:08:29,980 --> 00:08:32,900
Which one is the real Straw Hat?!

95
00:08:36,180 --> 00:08:38,740
Monkey D. Luffy...

96
00:08:39,290 --> 00:08:42,250
I'll remember that name.

97
00:08:42,250 --> 00:08:45,420
Come! To the New World!

98
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:51,840
What a stupid story...

99
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:54,800
You're the one who hasn't become

100
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,470
king of the pirates.

101
00:08:58,580 --> 00:09:01,300
I'm here to pick another fight with you!

102
00:09:01,310 --> 00:09:04,850
Don't be cocky just because
you're an emperor!

103
00:09:04,850 --> 00:09:07,310
I'm going to take Sanji back!

104
00:09:07,310 --> 00:09:11,420
And in the end, we're the ones who'll win!

105
00:09:18,060 --> 00:09:22,020
The cake has... collapsed...

106
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:34,550
Dammit...

107
00:09:35,950 --> 00:09:38,760
Dammit...

108
00:09:41,350 --> 00:09:45,940
How dare he ruin my wedding cake!

109
00:09:49,050 --> 00:09:53,820
Which one's the real Straw Hat Luffy?!

110
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:57,550
Where is he?!

111
00:09:58,570 --> 00:10:02,410
What an idiot.
This is just a diversion.

112
00:10:02,410 --> 00:10:06,080
Show yourself! Straw Hat!

113
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,970
Does she really expect him to reveal himself?

114
00:10:08,970 --> 00:10:11,460
I mean, if he responds...

115
00:10:22,700 --> 00:10:26,070
It's me!

116
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:31,400
He... He responded!

117
00:10:32,220 --> 00:10:35,900
There you are, Straw Hat...

118
00:10:35,900 --> 00:10:38,700
I'll crush you!

119
00:10:54,670 --> 00:10:57,300
There's the picture frame!

120
00:11:05,680 --> 00:11:09,810
Vito... Gotti...
Are the launchers ready?

121
00:11:11,280 --> 00:11:16,180
Yes, we can jump out anytime, Father.

122
00:11:17,440 --> 00:11:20,400
Straw Hat... Do your best.

123
00:11:20,780 --> 00:11:22,430
No, let go of me!

124
00:11:22,430 --> 00:11:24,880
The flock keeps coming!

125
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:30,700
Come on!

126
00:11:34,390 --> 00:11:37,000
That must be the real Luffy.

127
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:40,580
Once Luffy breaks the picture,
we'll burst in after three seconds...

128
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:41,970
Uh-huh...

129
00:11:41,970 --> 00:11:44,760
Are you listening? Be serious!

130
00:11:45,100 --> 00:11:46,880
Uh-huh...

131
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:50,180
Zeus!

132
00:11:50,180 --> 00:11:51,520
Yes, Mama!

133
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:52,950
Prometheus!

134
00:11:52,950 --> 00:11:54,400
Yes, Mama!

135
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:56,900
I'll take them all out at once!

136
00:11:59,780 --> 00:12:00,860
Okay!

137
00:12:03,490 --> 00:12:04,570
This'll be easy!

138
00:12:04,570 --> 00:12:06,830
Take this!

139
00:12:06,830 --> 00:12:08,120
He can do it!

140
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:10,500
Gum-Gum...

141
00:12:12,960 --> 00:12:15,100
What?!

142
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:19,380
This is the real one!

143
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:22,540
The other versions of Straw Hat are

144
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:28,560
just animals from the island
that were transformed by Brûlée's ability.

145
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:30,080
Ignore them!

146
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:33,230
I see! So they used Brûlée's ability!

147
00:12:34,230 --> 00:12:35,350
Damn...

148
00:12:37,060 --> 00:12:38,770
What the hell is this?!

149
00:12:38,770 --> 00:12:42,480
My limbs are buried and I can't pull them out!
What kind of ability is this?!

150
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:45,700
Katakuri! You think I need help?

151
00:12:45,700 --> 00:12:48,740
You're my son; I don't need...

152
00:12:47,250 --> 00:12:48,740
No, Mama!

153
00:12:48,740 --> 00:12:49,360
Huh?

154
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:52,080
He was targeting...

155
00:12:56,040 --> 00:12:59,590
Mother Carmel's portrait.

156
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:05,580
How do you know its importance to us?

157
00:13:05,580 --> 00:13:08,440
I thought only our allies knew.

158
00:13:10,300 --> 00:13:12,370
Spit it out! Who told you?

159
00:13:12,370 --> 00:13:14,850
Shut up!
Let go of me, you idiot!

160
00:13:14,850 --> 00:13:17,600
Damn... The plan's in ruins.

161
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:20,320
Somebody! Just break the picture!

162
00:13:29,970 --> 00:13:30,950
Luffy!

163
00:13:30,950 --> 00:13:32,390
Damn.

164
00:13:32,390 --> 00:13:33,750
I'll handle it, Pedro!

165
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:39,560
Ocean Current...

166
00:13:39,560 --> 00:13:42,080
Shoulder Throw!

167
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,590
Run!

168
00:14:00,270 --> 00:14:03,380
Don't explain my powers to them...

169
00:14:03,690 --> 00:14:05,310
That was close...

170
00:14:05,310 --> 00:14:08,950
Katakuri ate a special paramecia fruit.

171
00:14:08,950 --> 00:14:11,630
The Mochi-Mochi Fruit.

172
00:14:11,630 --> 00:14:12,450
Jinbe!

173
00:14:12,450 --> 00:14:17,320
You can escape if there's enough moisture,
but try not to touch it instead.

174
00:14:17,700 --> 00:14:18,960
Jinbe?

175
00:14:18,960 --> 00:14:24,000
I'm the one who told Luffy
about Mother Carmel.

176
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:28,240
I heard all about it
while I was working under you.

177
00:14:32,130 --> 00:14:36,020
Those idiots!
How dare they interfere...

178
00:14:36,020 --> 00:14:40,000
To come this far to take Sanji back!

179
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,270
The wedding has been ruined...

180
00:14:42,270 --> 00:14:45,260
I thought that silly Straw Hat was dead...

181
00:14:45,260 --> 00:14:49,150
Don't worry, Vinsmokes.

182
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:53,410
The Charlotte family will handle this...

183
00:14:53,740 --> 00:14:55,500
Lick!

184
00:14:58,620 --> 00:15:00,340
You...

185
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:04,040
I thought you decided not to leave my crew,

186
00:15:04,040 --> 00:15:08,900
yet now you're sticking up for this cake wrecker?

187
00:15:09,740 --> 00:15:14,550
Shall I take this as a rebellion,

188
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:16,090
Jinbe?

189
00:15:16,090 --> 00:15:18,800
Yes, that's exactly what this is.

190
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:22,660
You have some nerve...

191
00:15:23,810 --> 00:15:27,360
I wish to end our agreement...

192
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:35,280
and join the Straw Hat Pirates!

193
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:37,990
What?!

194
00:15:42,120 --> 00:15:44,460
This is big news!

195
00:15:44,460 --> 00:15:48,300
The former warlord Jinbe
is joining the Straw Hat crew!

196
00:15:50,960 --> 00:15:55,390
That's okay...
You can do whatever you want.

197
00:15:55,720 --> 00:16:01,340
But first you have to pay the price to leave.

198
00:16:01,340 --> 00:16:05,270
You don't want to live in shame,
do you?

199
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:06,680
Right...

200
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:11,110
If you promise that
you won't hurt anyone else,

201
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:15,540
I'll happily give you as much 
of my lifespan as you can take!

202
00:16:16,160 --> 00:16:20,520
Hey, what are you talking about, Jinbe?!
You can't join my crew if you're dead!

203
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:24,950
I love to take people's lifespans!

204
00:16:25,550 --> 00:16:29,660
I see...
I never realized you hated me so much.

205
00:16:29,660 --> 00:16:35,430
You'd rather choose death
than stay somewhere you don't want to be...

206
00:16:35,430 --> 00:16:37,700
so I won't show any mercy!

207
00:16:39,930 --> 00:16:43,350
Oh... Here it is again!
The Soul Pocus!

208
00:16:44,350 --> 00:16:47,860
All right! You've got a deal!

209
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:53,240
You fool...

210
00:16:54,650 --> 00:16:56,820
Stay...

211
00:17:02,330 --> 00:17:04,120
or...

212
00:17:04,120 --> 00:17:06,590
life?

213
00:17:09,830 --> 00:17:11,840
Life!

214
00:17:12,130 --> 00:17:13,450
Mama...

215
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:15,920
It... can't be stopped now...

216
00:17:15,920 --> 00:17:18,720
Is Jinbe really going to die here...?

217
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:21,350
Go to hell...

218
00:17:39,150 --> 00:17:41,800
Stay or...

219
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,450
life!

220
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:51,070
H-His soul isn't coming out of his body!

221
00:17:51,070 --> 00:17:55,260
You're kidding me...
He's showing no fear in front of Mama!

222
00:17:57,920 --> 00:18:00,140
Of course not.

223
00:18:00,470 --> 00:18:05,230
I intend to join the crew
of the future pirate king...

224
00:18:07,270 --> 00:18:10,900
A mere emperor
does not scare me!

225
00:18:17,450 --> 00:18:20,620
Mama... can't take his lifespan?

226
00:18:31,030 --> 00:18:33,340
If you will not take my life...

227
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:37,880
then I shall return your ritual sake cup.

228
00:18:48,210 --> 00:18:54,070
As of this moment,
I am leaving the Big Mom Pirates!

229
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:58,180
Thank you for all you've done!

230
00:19:06,490 --> 00:19:09,220
I can't believe he's doing it right now...

231
00:19:09,220 --> 00:19:12,280
So cool... Jinbe...

232
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:17,600
All right!

233
00:19:33,100 --> 00:19:36,100
Congratulations, Jinbe...

234
00:19:39,010 --> 00:19:43,360
but this means you're my enemy now, right?

235
00:19:45,480 --> 00:19:46,500
Jinbe!

236
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:48,360
Go to hell!

237
00:20:05,490 --> 00:20:07,740
Look! Over there!

238
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:17,020
H-He broke the... portrait of Mother Carmel!

239
00:20:25,240 --> 00:20:29,460
Oh, no! This is a big deal!

240
00:20:30,250 --> 00:20:31,380
Mama...

241
00:20:34,030 --> 00:20:35,760
Yes!

242
00:20:35,760 --> 00:20:38,000
All right!

243
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:39,410
It's broken!

244
00:20:40,340 --> 00:20:45,460
What the hell?!
I thought the fake Straw Hats were all animals!

245
00:20:53,900 --> 00:20:58,780
Okay! Big Mom has seen the broken picture!

246
00:20:58,780 --> 00:21:01,770
Now, if she just shrieks...

247
00:21:08,360 --> 00:21:10,520
What is he doing?

248
00:21:15,370 --> 00:21:19,490
This deadly poison KX launcher
is ready to fire-rero!

249
00:21:28,320 --> 00:21:30,560
He ripped off his face!

250
00:21:30,560 --> 00:21:33,280
No! This is my real face!

251
00:21:33,280 --> 00:21:35,120
Gross!

252
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:35,900
What...?

253
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:39,680
S-Soul King?!

254
00:21:40,490 --> 00:21:43,700
I thought that you were dead!

255
00:21:43,700 --> 00:21:47,340
I am... But that happened a long time ago.

256
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:50,780
Do you know...

257
00:21:50,780 --> 00:21:53,740
who that is...

258
00:21:57,370 --> 00:22:01,340
in that picture...?

259
00:22:01,870 --> 00:22:04,290
M-Mother...

260
00:22:05,200 --> 00:22:08,000
W-Why isn't she shrieking?

261
00:22:11,090 --> 00:22:15,930
Oh, no! It's just like the other day!
Mama's gonna go on a rampage!

262
00:22:16,130 --> 00:22:20,800
Do you have any idea who that is?

263
00:22:22,840 --> 00:22:27,480
And the wedding cake!

264
00:22:30,190 --> 00:22:33,320
Oh, so that's it!

265
00:22:35,780 --> 00:22:38,530
Mama's not thinking straight!
She's gonna have a tantrum!

266
00:22:38,530 --> 00:22:41,430
Kill Straw Hat and the others
before that happens!

267
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:43,900
Luffy!

268
00:22:43,900 --> 00:22:47,590
We have to survive until Big Mom panics!

269
00:22:47,590 --> 00:22:48,380
Okay!

270
00:22:48,380 --> 00:22:50,650
Straw Hat!

271
00:22:56,670 --> 00:22:57,660
Help!

272
00:22:57,660 --> 00:23:01,140
Stop it! Get off of me!

273
00:23:10,360 --> 00:23:12,310
Are you okay, Pudding-chan ?

274
00:23:12,310 --> 00:23:14,860
Let's get you somewhere safe.

275
00:23:42,310 --> 00:23:43,970
Stop, Pudding-chan !

276
00:23:43,970 --> 00:23:45,770
Shut up!

277
00:23:46,600 --> 00:23:50,310
Look! This is who I truly am!

278
00:23:51,190 --> 00:23:54,830
Aren't you shocked and disappointed?!

279
00:23:54,830 --> 00:23:57,060
Don't worry.

280
00:23:57,060 --> 00:23:59,370
You'll be dead soon!

281
00:24:16,300 --> 00:24:20,710
I've fooled many people like this!

282
00:24:20,710 --> 00:24:22,420
Including yourself?!

283
00:24:23,650 --> 00:24:29,630
You've been fooling yourself,
haven't you, Pudding-chan ?

284
00:24:30,880 --> 00:24:34,200
Sh... Shut up!

285
00:24:34,200 --> 00:24:36,620
An idiot like you can't...

286
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:44,630
An idiot like you can't...

287
00:24:45,700 --> 00:24:47,630
Move aside, Pudding!

288
00:24:58,360 --> 00:24:59,510
Pudding-chan !

289
00:25:08,670 --> 00:25:10,530
Are you okay, Pudding-chan ?

290
00:25:10,530 --> 00:25:14,340
You blew it! You're useless!

291
00:25:14,340 --> 00:25:16,490
Big Brother Daifuku!

292
00:25:17,290 --> 00:25:22,950
We needed you to kill the groom.

293
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:28,620
Let go of me!

294
00:25:33,570 --> 00:25:35,880
Go, jinni!

295
00:25:41,200 --> 00:25:42,770
Jinni!

296
00:25:49,100 --> 00:25:50,400
What's that?!

297
00:25:52,940 --> 00:25:54,670
Brother Daifuku!

298
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:58,950
Wait! I promise I'll get it done!

299
00:26:01,230 --> 00:26:05,830
You couldn't do it then...
You won't do it now!

300
00:26:10,660 --> 00:26:11,750
Pudding-chan !

301
00:26:17,940 --> 00:26:20,680
Jinn-uinely Enraged Cleave

302
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:24,050
Collier Strike!

303
00:26:37,600 --> 00:26:40,360
Stop!

304
00:26:40,360 --> 00:26:44,880
Don't abuse my powers anymore!

305
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:48,840
Shut up! My heart is at stake!

306
00:26:54,040 --> 00:26:56,440
These guys just won't stop.

307
00:26:59,110 --> 00:27:01,350
What are you doing, Bege?!

308
00:27:01,350 --> 00:27:06,890
Be quiet! I'm the head of security!
They'll suspect me if I do nothing!

309
00:27:06,890 --> 00:27:08,900
I got the captain!

310
00:27:08,900 --> 00:27:11,130
Alright! Kill him!

311
00:27:12,790 --> 00:27:16,020
That might not be a bad idea.

312
00:27:16,020 --> 00:27:17,900
Screw you!

313
00:27:18,710 --> 00:27:21,950
Listen! We're in trouble.

314
00:27:22,840 --> 00:27:25,580
Why isn't Big Mom shrieking?!

315
00:27:27,810 --> 00:27:29,830
I can't fight this many!

316
00:27:32,660 --> 00:27:33,920
Jinbe!

317
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:35,650
Oven!

318
00:27:37,940 --> 00:27:39,300
You bastard!

319
00:27:39,300 --> 00:27:43,340
Hey, Pedro!
Don't let him land any hits on you!

320
00:27:48,590 --> 00:27:50,160
Wha... What the...?!

321
00:27:55,740 --> 00:27:59,110
I remember you, Pedro!

322
00:27:59,110 --> 00:28:02,440
Pekoms calls you his big brother.

323
00:28:02,970 --> 00:28:07,850
You failed to steal Mama's poneglyph.

324
00:28:07,850 --> 00:28:11,410
You lost an eye and years of your lifespan as a result.

325
00:28:12,690 --> 00:28:16,400
Yet you've returned here,
despite the limited time you have left...

326
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:18,950
So you're prepared to die, right?

327
00:28:25,910 --> 00:28:28,940
I've always been prepared!

328
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:32,440
I'll burn you to death!

329
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:36,730
It's been way longer than three seconds!

330
00:28:37,320 --> 00:28:39,500
What's going on?

331
00:28:39,500 --> 00:28:42,200
She's not shrieking at all!

332
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:56,880
Brook!

333
00:28:57,380 --> 00:29:01,870
I'm okay. I'm alive.
I mean, I'm dead...

334
00:29:02,580 --> 00:29:05,560
I didn't know you could do that!

335
00:29:08,010 --> 00:29:10,700
Anyway, listen to me, Luffy-san !

336
00:29:10,700 --> 00:29:13,940
What the hell are you doing?!

337
00:29:13,940 --> 00:29:18,900
How could you do this to us!

338
00:29:18,900 --> 00:29:21,570
Oh, no! Bege, get off of me!

339
00:29:23,150 --> 00:29:25,910
Damn! This wasn't supposed to happen.

340
00:29:26,410 --> 00:29:29,140
Tell me this is a mistake!

341
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:31,420
Big Mom!

342
00:29:35,500 --> 00:29:37,830
Lick.

343
00:29:39,320 --> 00:29:44,620
I trusted you! Even the underworld
is ruled by honor and decency!

344
00:29:45,950 --> 00:29:47,800
Say something!

345
00:29:51,060 --> 00:29:54,440
Don't be pathetic, Father.

346
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:56,500
It's already too late for us.

347
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:59,390
We're trapped by this candy.

348
00:30:00,180 --> 00:30:04,660
And they already took all of our weapons.
We don't even have our raid suits.

349
00:30:04,660 --> 00:30:09,460
We've been totally set up.
I guess we were too ambitious.

350
00:30:13,400 --> 00:30:16,580
What's so funny, you fools?!

351
00:30:19,240 --> 00:30:24,240
The one who removed all empathy from your sons was you,

352
00:30:24,460 --> 00:30:26,080
Father.

353
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:29,980
They don't even fear their own deaths...

354
00:30:30,730 --> 00:30:35,370
They're my younger brothers,
but even I can't call them human.

355
00:30:38,940 --> 00:30:43,900
Oh, boy. I've never seen
such a pathetic assassination!

356
00:30:43,900 --> 00:30:48,120
This feels more like
a cruel execution. Lick.

357
00:30:49,740 --> 00:30:53,560
Don't you agree, Judge?

358
00:30:54,480 --> 00:30:58,560
I have... devoted my whole life...

359
00:30:58,560 --> 00:31:00,790
my very existence...

360
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:04,900
toward getting revenge on the countries
in the North Blue!

361
00:31:04,900 --> 00:31:09,360
To restore the Empire of Germa!

362
00:31:09,360 --> 00:31:11,390
Big Mom!

363
00:31:11,890 --> 00:31:16,950
Say something, Big Mom!!

364
00:31:20,710 --> 00:31:23,400
Look at yourself!

365
00:31:23,400 --> 00:31:27,000
What? Germa's gonna get wiped out?

366
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:30,660
Oh! This is big news!

367
00:31:37,850 --> 00:31:41,110
He's crying!

368
00:31:43,940 --> 00:31:48,800
Tell me... it's not true!

369
00:31:48,800 --> 00:31:52,430
It's no use. Look at Mama.

370
00:31:52,890 --> 00:31:57,410
She's dazed by these shocking events.

371
00:31:52,890 --> 00:31:57,410
Mother... Cake...

372
00:31:58,150 --> 00:32:03,160
It made me a little nervous
when the portrait of Mother Carmel was broken,

373
00:32:03,160 --> 00:32:09,660
but the intensity of her anger
has overwhelmed her grief, so we're okay.

374
00:32:10,150 --> 00:32:15,790
I truly understand
your burning ambition, Judge...

375
00:32:15,790 --> 00:32:17,070
Lick.

376
00:32:17,580 --> 00:32:24,520
But do you listen to what a cow has to say
when you're about to eat it?

377
00:32:27,330 --> 00:32:33,540
Your death will nourish us,
Germa 66!

378
00:32:34,950 --> 00:32:36,770
Sanji's family...

379
00:32:36,770 --> 00:32:39,670
Luffy-san, listen to me!

380
00:32:39,670 --> 00:32:43,360
Big Mom has experienced too many shocks
in quick succession,

381
00:32:43,360 --> 00:32:46,920
so she doesn't know
how to focus her anger.

382
00:32:46,920 --> 00:32:51,070
We should show her the broken portrait again!

383
00:32:51,070 --> 00:32:54,320
Okay! I'll do it if you think it's best!

384
00:32:54,320 --> 00:32:56,660
Hey, isn't it too late...?

385
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:01,790
What's wrong?

386
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:04,950
That guy from earlier is coming!

387
00:33:07,280 --> 00:33:09,010
Katakuri!

388
00:33:10,400 --> 00:33:14,980
All right! Carry on! That plan will work!

389
00:33:15,470 --> 00:33:18,590
Katakuri is looking pale!

390
00:33:18,590 --> 00:33:23,060
That means he's seen a future
where things get messy.

391
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:25,240
Go, Straw Hat!

392
00:33:25,240 --> 00:33:26,930
Okay!

393
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:29,360
Jinbe! Pedro!

394
00:33:29,360 --> 00:33:32,850
We gotta back Straw Hat up
with all we've got! Follow me!

395
00:33:40,470 --> 00:33:42,280
Allied forces!

396
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:48,190
All of you,
get your Invisible Symphonia ready!

397
00:33:48,190 --> 00:33:49,810
– Invi...
– Oh!

398
00:33:49,810 --> 00:33:51,200
The earplugs!

399
00:33:51,200 --> 00:33:52,560
Bege?

400
00:33:52,560 --> 00:33:55,500
What did he yell out all of a sudden?!

401
00:33:57,230 --> 00:33:58,770
Can you make it?!

402
00:33:58,770 --> 00:34:03,970
Will it work in time?! Our only chance is to
neutralize everyone with a gun all at once!

403
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:08,720
Bege!

404
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:16,810
Shoot Straw Hat to death now!

405
00:34:19,470 --> 00:34:21,610
I refuse.

406
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:36,610
All right! If I show this to Big Mom again,
the plan's back on track, right?

407
00:34:46,680 --> 00:34:50,040
Flambage Shot!

408
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:06,490
You can see slightly ahead into the future.

409
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:10,950
But even if we can't see it,

410
00:35:11,460 --> 00:35:14,410
we all have the right...

411
00:35:14,880 --> 00:35:18,690
to change the future!

412
00:35:22,280 --> 00:35:27,800
S... traw... Ha... t...!

